Comment.Text: Step 1: Ensure that OpenViBE Acquisition Server is running and broadcasting data
Step 3: Change "Spatial filter configuration" to a CSP saved from Train CSP (i.e. Kyl014_Trn1_6D_CSP.cfg)
Step 2: Change "Filename" to where you want to save the EEG data (i.e. Kyl014_Trn1.ov)
Step 4: Change "Filename to load configuration from" to a LDA classifier saved from Train Classifier (i.e. Kyl014_Trn1_LDA.cfg)
